    <title>环境配置</title>
    <link href="https://zer01s.work/2023/07/20/%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/"/>
    <id>https://zer01s.work/2023/07/20/%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</id>
    <published>2023-07-20T14:00:37.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-07-20T14:07:20.829Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="WSL2-Install-Ubuntu-18-04"><a href="#WSL2-Install-Ubuntu-18-04" class="headerlink" title="WSL2 Install Ubuntu-18.04"></a>WSL2 Install Ubuntu-18.04</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wsl -l -o</span><br><span class="line">wsl --install -d Ubuntu-18.04</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>因为wsl -l -o的发行版没有16.04的Ubuntu</p><h3 id="change-source-list"><a href="#change-source-list" class="headerlink" title="change source.list"></a>change source.list</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo nano /etc/apt/sources.list</span><br><span class="line"># 18.04 清华源</span><br><span class="line">deb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/ubuntu/ bionic main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/ubuntu/ bionic-updates main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/ubuntu/ bionic-backports main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/ubuntu/ bionic-security main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line"># update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt upgrade</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Toolchain"><a href="#Toolchain" class="headerlink" title="Toolchain"></a>Toolchain</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install -y build-essential gdb</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install -y gcc-multilib</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="qemu"><a href="#qemu" class="headerlink" title="qemu"></a>qemu</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install -y libpixman-1-dev pkg-config zlib1g-dev libglib2.0-dev python</span><br><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/mit-pdos/6.828-qemu.git qemu</span><br><span class="line">cd qemu</span><br><span class="line">./configure --disable-kvm --target-list=&quot;i386-softmmu x86_64-softmmu&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>QEMU will install to &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local by default</p><h4 id="Q-amp-A："><a href="#Q-amp-A：" class="headerlink" title="Q&amp;A："></a>Q&amp;A：</h4><p>● VSCODE-WSL2的写权限：<br>sudo chown -R $USER &#x2F;home<br>● make error<br><a class="link"   href="https://github.com/woai3c/MIT6.828/blob/master/docs/install.md" >https://github.com/woai3c/MIT6.828/blob/master/docs/install.md<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a><br>● make sucess</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">qemu-system-i386 --version</span><br><span class="line">QEMU emulator version 2.3.0, Copyright (c) 2003-2008 Fabrice Bellard</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Reference"><a href="#Reference" class="headerlink" title="Reference:"></a>Reference:</h3><p><a class="link"   href="https://pdos.csail.mit.edu/6.828/2018/tools.html" >https://pdos.csail.mit.edu/6.828/2018/tools.html<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
